<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l5">von der <expan>drey<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Tawſt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wır Jn auſgeſant <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l6">mıt dem <expan>kamr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu prag <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>r</expan> gearbeyt hab / daʒ er den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tag ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l7">Jn <expan>beſchıd<ex>en</ex></expan> hab ʒum <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> gen prag auf den <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> mentag nach ſand </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l8"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> tag etc . Nu ıſt vns <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſein <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> als heẅt fünf hor auf den </ab>
