<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l10">prag <expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> . Denn <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ıſt vnd <expan>empfelhe<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l11">daʒ Jr dem <expan>Neẅſtett<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>darinn<ex>en</ex></expan> hılfflıch ſeyt . <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fleıſſ vnd ernſt </ab>
